'''子宫脱垂'''是[[女性生殖器脱垂|女性生殖器脱垂]]的一种。

==病理及病因==
正常情况下，[[子宫|子宫]]由[[肌肉|肌肉]]和[[韧带|韧带]]在上牵扯固定。而当韧带的拉力变弱，子宫下滑，不能保持在正常位置，则子宫脱垂便发生了。固定子宫的韧带包括[[圆韧带|圆韧带]]、[[子宫骶韧带|子宫骶韧带]]、[[阔韧带|阔韧带]]以及[[卵巢韧带|卵巢韧带]]。而子宫骶韧带对于防止子宫脱垂起着尤为重要的作用。

子宫脱垂最常见的病因是[[分娩|分娩]]时的外伤，尤其是多胎或[[难产|难产]]。大约50%的产后妇女有着或多或少的盆腔器官脱垂。{{Citation needed|date=April 2012}}而年龄越大，这些现象越为明显，尤其是[[更年期|更年期]]后的女性。这些情况可以通过[[外科手术|外科手术]]进行矫正。

==治疗==
手术治疗包括{{fact|[[子宮切除術|子宮切除術]]}}，[[子宫骶骨固定术|子宫骶骨固定术]](sacrohysteropexy)<ref>Price N, Slack A, Jackson S. Laparoscopic hysteropexy: the initial results of a uterine suspension procedure for uterovaginal prolapse. BJOG 2010;117:62–68. {{doi|10.1111/j.1471-0528.2009.02396}}. www.bjog.org</ref>，[[曼彻斯特手术|曼彻斯特手术]]<ref>[https://www.icsoffice.org/Abstracts/Publish/47/000534.pdf Surgical correction of uterine prolapse: cervical amputation with uterosacral ligament plication versus vaginal hysterectomy with high uterosacral ligament plication] {{Wayback|url=https://www.icsoffice.org/Abstracts/Publish/47/000534.pdf |date=20111008185530 }} By de Boer T, Milani F, Kluivers K, Withagen M, Vierhout M. Part of [http://www.urotoday.com/images/conferences/ics_2009/ics_2009_scientificprogramme.pdf ICS 2009 Scientific Programme, Thursday 1 October 2009] {{Wayback|url=http://www.urotoday.com/images/conferences/ics_2009/ics_2009_scientificprogramme.pdf |date=20111008185530 }}</ref> 

{{anchor|sacrocolpopexy}}
在切除子宫的手术中，可以进行[[阴道骶骨固定术|阴道骶骨固定术]](sacrocolpopexy)，使阴道顶端与骶骨连接。<ref>[http://publications.nice.org.uk/sacrocolpopexy-with-hysterectomy-using-mesh-for-uterine-prolapse-repair-ipg284/the-procedure NICE interventional procedure guidance IPG284: Sacrocolpopexy with hysterectomy using mesh for uterine prolapse repair] {{Wayback|url=http://publications.nice.org.uk/sacrocolpopexy-with-hysterectomy-using-mesh-for-uterine-prolapse-repair-ipg284/the-procedure |date=20150518091958 }} by the [[National_Institute_for_Health_and_Care_Excellence|National Institute for Health and Care Excellence]], Issued: January 2009</ref>

